title: FRAM Fresh Breeze Cabin Air Filter Replacement for Car Passenger Compartment w/ Arm and Hammer Baking Soda, Easy Install, CF10134 for Honda Vehicles
description: The FRAM Fresh Breeze cabin air filter is the only cabin air filter that uses the natural deodorizing properties of ARM & HAMMER baking soda and activated carbon embedded in the filter. FRAM recommends changing your cabin air filter every 12,000 miles.
